title: DigitalTutors - Creating and Integrating Weather Elements in May
description:
Digital Tutors - Creating and Integrating Weather Elements in Maya

Throughout this Maya tutorial we'll create dynamic weather effect from start to finish. Starting with a piece of live action footage, we'll create a match move camera, then we'll set up rain and blowing leaves using Maya nParticles. We'll finish by rendering our simulations out in V-Ray and composite them over our footage in NUKE. After completing this Maya training, you'll have created your own dynamic weather elements, that'll help you effectively change the look and feel of your own videos
